Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 20:07:18 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add Docker setup and fix local configuration

- Dockerfile: two-stage build, copies client_side into jar as static assets
- docker-compose.yml: single command startup, persistent submissions volume
- pom.xml: include ../client_side as Spring Boot static resources
- application.properties: set server.port=8080, remove stale prod URLs
- SubmissionController: add localhost:8080 to all CrossOrigin origins
- users/experts_panel.json: demo credentials for local testing
- README: rewrite with Docker and non-Docker instructions, correct entry points
